OL,3,CItalian parliament votes to make
OL,4,Cfemicide a crime
OL,6,FItaly's parliament on Tuesday approved
OL,7,Fa law that introduces femicide into
OL,8,Fthe country's criminal code and
OL,9,Fpunishes it with life in prison.
OL,11,FThe vote coincided with the
OL,12,FInternational Day for the Elimination
OL,13,Fof Violence against Women, a day
OL,14,Fdesignated by the UN General Assembly.
OL,16,FThe law won bipartisan support from
OL,17,Fthe center-right majority and the
OL,18,Fcenter-left opposition in the final
OL,19,Fvote in the Lower Chamber, passing
OL,20,Fwith 237 votes in favor.
