OL,3,CItalian parliament votes to make
OL,4,Cfemicide a crime
OL,6,FThe law, backed by the conservative
OL,7,Fgovernment of Premier Giorgia Meloni,
OL,8,Fcomes in response to a series of
OL,9,Fkillings and other violence targeting
OL,10,Fwomen in Italy.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FIt includes stronger measures against
OL,18,Fgender-based crimes, including
OL,19,Fstalking and image-based abuse, also
OL,20,Fknown as revenge porn.
