OL,6,FMeloni said: "We have doubled funding
OL,7,Ffor anti-violence centers and
OL,8,Fshelters, promoted an emergency
OL,9,Fhotline, and implemented innovative
OL,10,Feducation and awareness-raising
OL,11,Factivities.
OL,13,F"These are concrete steps forward, but
OL,14,Fwe won't stop here. We must continue
OL,15,Fto do much more, every day."
