OL,6,FWhile the center-left opposition
OL,7,Fsupported the law in parliament, it
OL,8,Fstressed that the government's
OL,9,Fapproach only tackles the criminal
OL,10,Faspect of the problem while leaving
OL,11,Feconomic and cultural divides
OL,12,Funaddressed.
OL,14,FItaly's statistics agency Istat
OL,15,Frecorded 106 femicides in 2024, 62 of
OL,16,Fwhich were committed by partners or
OL,17,Fformer partners.
