OL,6,FAccording to the European Institute
OL,7,Ffor Gender Equality, there is no
OL,8,Fdefinition of femicide in UK criminal
OL,9,Flaw.
OL,11,FHowever, this type of offence may fall
OL,12,Funder other provisions of the law,
OL,13,Fsuch as murder or manslaughter.
OL,15,FMurder and manslaughter are two of the
OL,16,Foffences that constitute homicide.
